Package me.kverna.roger.server.video

Class VideoDetectionTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.kverna.roger.server.video.VideoDetectionTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, VideoFeedListener
    public class VideoDetectionTask
extends java.lang.Object
implements VideoFeedListener, java.lang.Runnable
    A long-lived task for detecting circles in an attached video feed task.

    In the future, this could use some interface implementation to handle different kinds of detection.
